♪Waiting for the fragrance of flowers♪

00:15:50.620 --> 00:15:53.550
♪To cross over the high wall♪

00:15:55.260 --> 00:15:58.670
♪Waiting for the shore♪

00:15:59.430 --> 00:16:03.240
♪To forget the storm♪

00:16:04.360 --> 00:16:07.880
♪Just like this♪

00:16:08.670 --> 00:16:12.060
♪Wasting a few inches♪

00:16:12.060 --> 00:16:13.380
♪Of daylight♪

00:16:13.630 --> 00:16:16.790
♪Half for the memories♪

00:16:18.260 --> 00:16:22.140
♪Half for the dreams♪

00:16:22.730 --> 00:16:24.830
♪Oh, little boat♪

00:16:25.020 --> 00:16:27.150
♪Where are you going♪

00:16:27.530 --> 00:16:31.430
♪No need to answer that♪

00:16:31.940 --> 00:16:34.160
♪Just let me♪

00:16:34.350 --> 00:16:36.380
♪Watch you drift away♪

00:16:36.380 --> 00:16:40.600
♪Into the sunset glow♪

00:16:41.130 --> 00:16:43.290
♪Don't be afraid♪

00:16:43.520 --> 00:16:45.610
♪This world♪

00:16:45.850 --> 00:16:49.890
♪Is vast as it may be♪

00:16:50.500 --> 00:16:52.780
♪But there's always♪

00:16:52.780 --> 00:16:54.800
♪Someone who cares♪

00:16:54.800 --> 00:16:58.750
♪Shining like a lighthouse♪